web-server.js — HTTP API + static file serving for mcp-agent-portal

startWebServer(projectRoot)→{server,proxyManager}|boot HTTP server, spawn MCP children, register gateway
serveStaticFile(reqPath,res)→void|serve static files from web/ or packages/ dirs

ROUTES:
  POST /api/mcp-call|proxy MCP tool call to child server
  GET /api/instances|list all registered MCP servers
  GET /api/project-info|portal metadata (name,path,agents,pid)
  GET /api/server-status|uptime,agents,monitors
  POST /api/stop|graceful shutdown exit(0)
  POST /api/restart|config-change restart exit(2)
  GET /api/*|fallback HTTP proxy to local-gateway backends

PATTERNS: fail-fast config|exit(2) restart|raw http.createServer|no framework
DEPS: local-gateway.js|mcp-proxy.js
